<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Development Resources</h1>
<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Here is a comprehensive list of all of the software, resources, documentation, and other tools we used. You can find attributions for any licensed materials we used as well.</p>

<section class="space-y-2">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold underline">Tools</h2>
    <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Production</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://about.google/products/">Google Products</a> — Google Drive, Google Sheets, Google Docs, Google Slides.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://git-scm.com/">Git</a> — Free and open source distributed version control system.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/about">Github</a> — The complete devloper platform to build, scale, and deliver secure software.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://miro.com/">Miro</a> — Collaborative AI workflows that help your team build the right thing, faster.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://discord.com/">Discord</a> — Group chat that's all fun & games.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/outlook/email-and-calendar-software-microsoft-outlook?deeplink=%2Fmail%2F0%2F&sdf=0">Outlook</a> — An email and calendar system by Micrrosoft.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://www.signupgenius.com/">SignUpGenius</a> — An easy sign up tool.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Game Engine + Addons</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://godotengine.org/">Godot Engine</a> — Free, open-source game engine.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://phantom-camera.dev/">Phantom Camera</a> — An addon that enhances the Godot camera.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/nathanhoad/godot_dialogue_manager">Godot Dialogue Manager</a> — An addon that provides a stateless branching dialgoue editor and runtime.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/limbonaut/limboai">LimboAI</a> — Behavior trees and state machines for Godot 4.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Art & UI</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://procreate.com/">Procreate</a> — App for digitial art.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://inkscape.org/">Inkscape</a> — Free vector image design tool.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://www.adobe.com/products/photoshop/landpa.html?sdid=NC5FRF5H&mv=search&mv2=paidsearch&ef_id=CjwKCAiAqprNBhB6EiwAMe3yhujczR1JSjnWvAqMN5HYhRnUVmchcIgYZP_0leh1NrY9ql8mVFqb0BoCI2sQAvD_BwE:G:s&s_kwcid=AL!3085!3!714745362176!e!!g!!adobe%20photoshop!1712238394!67643541820&mv=search&gad_source=1&gad_campaignid=1712238394&gclid=CjwKCAiAqprNBhB6EiwAMe3yhujczR1JSjnWvAqMN5HYhRnUVmchcIgYZP_0leh1NrY9ql8mVFqb0BoCI2sQAvD_BwE">Adobe Photoshop</a> — A image editing tool by Adobe</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://www.adobe.com/products/fresco.html">Adobe Fresco</a> — The pro painting and drawing app.</li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://www.photopea.com/">Photopea</a> — Free online photo editor./li>
      <li><a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" href="https://www.gimp.org/">GIMP</a> — GNU Image Manipulation Program.</li>
